data.description: $20K+ price drop on this Beautiful Swan Lake Estate with a Private Beach and Stunning Lake Views! This Unique Gem is situated on a 2.6-acre Park-Like Property boasting an impressive 426' of Lakeshore. The Gourmet Kitchen is a chef’s dream with Granite Countertops, Subzero Fridge, Five-Star Range with Double Ovens, an Indoor Grill and More. Enjoy the Breathtaking Lake Views from the Dining Room and Huge Deck. With 5BR, 3BA, a Walk-Out Lower Level, 2-Stall Garage, She-Shed, and Bonus Structure, this Property is Perfect for Entertaining and Relaxation. Recent Updates include a New Furnace/AC system, Roof, and Gutters. Sellers are also offering up to $20K in Credit Towards a New Septic. A Perfect Blend of Luxury and Comfort, it's a Must-See to Truly Appreciate the Beauty of this Swan Lake Gem.
